Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Warning,,0,0,0,,{\org(0,0)\fscx0\fscy0\clip(0,0,0,0)}Your media player does not support the subtitle format used in this episode.\NSubtitles will likely not function properly.\NPlease use one of the recommended video players, preferably mpv:\Nhttps://mpv.io
